stratego.components.friendslist

Class FriendModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • stratego.components.friendslist.FriendModel

  • public class FriendModel
extends java.util.Observable
    FriendsModel Object. A FriendModel is used in tandem with a FriendsList to create a functional friend list for a user. The FriendModel object is essentially an arraylist containing information about this users friend, and is used by FriendsList to generate a unique friend-list VBox.
